{"tid":1414103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌人放火唔等於割席","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:42:00.000Z","uid":58515,"like":55,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92c657335285a728c904bc109d2f8afa5573bb26","tid":1414103,"uid":58515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"出聲屌唔係次次都等於割席，可以係單統既提醒。<br />\n<br />\n最近幾次玩火魔法都可以見到啲魔法師都仍然好低lvl，連火都點唔著。咁既情況下一失手出事會好容易失控，最後甚至傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n應該反思下係咩情況先用咩手段，而且一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">安全第一</span>，唔好比情緒支配，淪落到野獸既lvl。"},{"pid":"6f8cdfdd021a929280af6a5bf03d084edcd24561","tid":1414103,"uid":60563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"要練習下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我肯定現場冇人有玩火經驗"},{"pid":"833094cd80596b273f29aaa4f36ab845c9223916","tid":1414103,"uid":128261,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"唔會反對用火，但真係要注意安全，唔可以比火勢蔓延傷到無辜市民<br />\n否則個運動遲早無以為繼"},{"pid":"eed8c9dd110873e6dda0eabdbe96995535ee9f0d","tid":1414103,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54152d09366a0453dc44adf1357f366994bf51d6","tid":1414103,"uid":58515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"833094cd80596b273f29aaa4f36ab845c9223916","tid":1414103,"uid":128261,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"唔會反對用火，但真係要注意安全，唔可以比火勢蔓延傷到無辜市民<br />\n否則個運動遲早無以為繼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"注意<span style=\"color: red;\">紀律部隊宿舍</span>唔係淨得狗住"},{"pid":"883ae72cf7f9d2c41b8de3c94826dab2a6040df0","tid":1414103,"uid":58515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"重申一次出聲屌不等於割席"},{"pid":"8bf7acc29e781d3059a47a9ab374a3c4e8ffb792","tid":1414103,"uid":247492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"做乜都好唔好俾人捉到<img src